summary: This new code file, moviepage2.html, contributes to the system by providing a user interface for displaying information about a specific movie ("Fight Club") and allowing users to rate the movie. The file includes HTML elements for the movie poster, summary, embedded video trailer, and a star rating system. Users can interact with the star ratings to submit their feedback on the movie, which is then displayed on the webpage. Additionally, the file incorporates navigation elements such as a home button and a hamburger menu for easy access to other pages in the system.
